{"word":"Nadab","slug":"nadab","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Nadab</b> <a href=\"#/H5070\">H5070</a> <br/> 1. Son of Aaron:<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=6&verse=23'>Exo 6:23</a> <br/> - Called to Mount Sinai with Moses and Aaron to worship<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=24&verse=1'>Exo 24:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=24&verse=10'>Exo 24:10</a> <br/> - Set apart to priesthood<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=28&verse=1'>Exo 28:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=28&verse=4'>Exo 28:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=28&verse=43'>Exo 28:43</a> <br/> - Offers strange fire to God, and is destroyed<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=10&verse=2'>Lev 10:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=3&verse=4'>Num 3:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=26&verse=61'>Num 26:61</a> <br/> - Is buried<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=10&verse=5'>Lev 10:5</a> <br/> - His father and brothers forbidden to mourn<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=10&verse=7'>Lev 10:7</a> <br/> 2. Son and successor of Jeroboam:<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=14&verse=20'>1Ki 14:20</a> <br/> - His wicked reign; murdered by Baasha<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=15&verse=31'>1Ki 15:31</a> <br/> 3. Great-grandson of Jerahmeel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=2&verse=28'>1Ch 2:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=2&verse=30'>1Ch 2:30</a><br/> 4. A Benjamite<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=8&verse=30'>1Ch 8:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=9&verse=36'>1Ch 9:36</a>"}]}